data.description: Charming Countryside Retreat: 3-Bedroom Home on 5 Acres! Features include: gorgeous checkered style fireplace with wood mantle, formal dining and living area, large windows, storm cellar, brick walkway to the large front porch. The kitchen is complete with white colored cabinetry, eat-in dining, an island, apron sink, and built-in ovens. The spacious primary bedroom includes a separate door for backyard access, an ensuite with double sink vanity, shower, and access to the generous sized walk-in closet. Enjoy your mornings and evenings on the screened porch. The home also includes a 30 x 50 workshop with a 10x10 office and half bath. Don’t miss out, schedule a showing today!
